Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把那些吃了 吃光了再来买
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\bord0\shad0\c&H596C5D&\pos(131,259)}大促销\N随意挑选\N3个\N{\fs36\c&H8D94D5&}350元{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦 今天还有那位猫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 说好了还要给阪本先生买饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么可以为您效劳的么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是雪人 今天刚进货的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话请选购
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜点？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似刨冰之类的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要买么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 只是看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是雪人么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不买那个的话就让给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明名乃可以买名乃的 却说博士不可以买博士的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 都说了这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么名乃可以买名乃的 所以博士也可以买博士的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}想要想要 想要嘛 想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 只能买一个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢名乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就买那种东西了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 又可爱 凉凉的又很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃 再来些…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我的饭在哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种饭 卡哧卡哧的 什么的

Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头 接下来是布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石剪布可不带哟 石头剪子布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝上走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发条！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\move(680,185,221,185)\c&HD4E6D2&}期中考试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO NO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(1250,285)}募\N集\N爵\N士\N空\N手\N道\N!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 考试结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天——呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是假发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}只{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想别人在追求什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为“别人”太多了 所以想不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想自己在追求什么的话 好像行得通不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:19.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\frz32.361\c&H122E53&\pos(529,342)}站前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:19.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\frz32.361\c&H122E53&\pos(642,431)}站前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:19.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\frz32.361\c&H122E53&\pos(694,471)}站前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:20.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\frz32.361\c&H122E53&\pos(731,514)}站前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有向某处的神明祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来某处的神明 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:43.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\fad(520,520)\pos(1180,360)\bord5\blur20}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不·倒·翁·公·公——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不罢手么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:05.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\shad1\4c&HF7F4F2&\pos(1080,360)}鹦\N鹉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被罚站了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个身体也 相当 适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是看着嘴里面就好多口水了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阪本先生 这是梅干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦 还没做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个跟阪本玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 逗猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本 阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我加上“先生”哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对哦 抱歉 阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你耍我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 一不小心… 对不起啊 阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫故意的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我去买东西了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这帮人真是没教养啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 阪本 不是故意的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 不是阪本！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 阪本 给你口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要让我说多少遍啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说你啊 哪有给猫口香糖的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 啊啊啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我差不多点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 之前我也说过了 我比你们年长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称呼年长的人要好好 加上“先生”  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 那个… 要说那个的话啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去尿尿可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦 快去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尿尿哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如所见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家里面果然只住着那两个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才这么没有教养
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家里面我就是最年长的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然麻烦 还是我来做他们的家长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我也是被一家不得了的捡去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 超开心啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本 你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被知道我在玩橡皮什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为家长的威严就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威严就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威严就……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像 有点睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪睡得真是多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 就是那么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么那么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那么回事 跟你说了这么多就是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 要从尊敬年长的人 开始 对吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 超开心——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本 再来一次 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本 阪本啊 快点快点 阪本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}不是 不对 刚才那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}我说 我不是说过了嘛 给我加上“先生”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全垒打！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？！

Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…倒翁公公 倒…了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒…翁公公…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣又装了一个这么难懂的傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法 总之先吐槽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣啊 那不是ON THE BOOK么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佑 再也不要吐这个槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这么好得吐了槽的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我装傻的部分就会被忽视的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 就是那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了不小心就会蹦出英语的年龄了 什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个“ON THE BOOK”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本来的样子还是在装傻很难懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 怎么说呢 反过来吐槽 什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在认真地说么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为是小佑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是小佑 所以我以为你会懂我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:18:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 头疼了啊 没想到你这么看我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被信任了还是很高兴的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以信任没信任什么的这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能算了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挚友之间 是无需多言的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是挚友 多说说话不也可以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太粘我的话 我很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说这种话的话 对小佑你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小佑你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变得 更加喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很好么 变得喜欢了 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挚友 哟 挚友！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是异性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却把你看作是异性…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不能很好的表达出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什 什…么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得 今天 有点不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时她也没这么多话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有说离着太近的话会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部 都是为了说这些话么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 从什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从什么时候 开始那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我 我 我说 麻 麻 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情 不是很好 之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事还是太早了 之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是高中生 之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我是在装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Ultra Bullet Wonderful 难以理解啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\an8}译注：此处捏森林好小子（燃える！お兄さん）中洛基的招式—\N—Super Ultra Bullet Wonderful Punch 该动画中文配音版中译成超级金刚无敌拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 奇怪的演技什么的少来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都相信了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为 因为是小佑 脑子转得很快所以会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 还是稍微明白了一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是 骗你什么的 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子“哔”的开始工作什么的 回转什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:20:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 仔细想想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你说的本身就很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 你不是说你相信了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那也是装傻…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经什么都察觉不到了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有察觉到么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还有一处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不知道啊 是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佑脑子转得很快 的那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该吐槽“根本不快”的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有那个地方非常 容易懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.81,0:22:07.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}朝起きて　歯を磨いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.81,0:22:07.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}早晨睡醒后 起床刷牙来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:10.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あっという間　午後10時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:10.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}不知不觉间 已到晚十点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:14.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も　たくさん　笑ったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:14.03,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天也遇到 很多欢乐事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:16.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}たくさん　ときめいたなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:16.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}也有非常多 刺激与紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:20.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}友達と　バカみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:20.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}和闺中密友 像笨蛋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:23.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}騒いでる　時にも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:23.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}大声吵又闹 偶尔会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:26.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}チラチラって　目が合う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:26.50,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}偶尔瞥向你 四目便相接
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:29.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}…偶然、だよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:29.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}这也不过是 偶然事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:32.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初恋なんて言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:32.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初恋什么的难以说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:35.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キャラじゃないんだもんっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:35.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}因为我不是这样的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:41.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ねえ　あしたも会えるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:41.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}呐 我们明天 也会相见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:44.93,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}まぶたを　閉じると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:44.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}将我的双眼 合上了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:48.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キラキラ　キミだらけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:48.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}脑海中只有 亮晶晶的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:51.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も　楽しかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:51.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天的我也 开心又愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:55.86,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あー　恋　してんだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:55.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}啊 陷入恋爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:03.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}うれしいな　うれしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:03.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}真的好开心 真的好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:06.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}はじめまして　こいごころ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:06.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}第一次见面 我的爱慕心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:10.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あした　まだ　あえるね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:10.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}到明天的话 我们又见面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}现在晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.42,0:23:17.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ゆめで　すぐ　あえるね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.42,0:23:17.46,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}在梦中很快 我们会见面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:23.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:23.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}现在晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有40年历史了哦 这个社区
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用汉字写一个“团地妻”试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\an8}译注：团地 相当于国内的社区 团地妻即指社区主妇\N至于为什么有特别的魅力 搜索一下 你就懂了= =
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 马上就会有一种特别的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话的日常是 第五话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待


